                    View the clinic in action.
                  </a>
                </p>
                <p class="lead">
                  Without our cheap vet treatment for low income pet owners it
                  is very likely that even more animals would be dumped or
                  handed over to the local dog warden &ndash; and very probably
                  put to sleep.
